&INFO
 Bulk Silicon.
 k-point calculation with 2 atoms (primitive cell)
 and a 2x2x2 MP-mesh.
&END

&CPMD
  OPTIMIZE WAVEFUNCTION
  CONVERGENCE ORBITALS
   1.0e-2
  PRINT FORCES ON
  MAXSTEP
  10
&END


&DFT
  FUNCTIONAL LDA
&END

&SYSTEM
  SYMMETRY
  FCC
  SCALE
  CELL
  10.263102 1.0  1.0  0  0  0
  CUTOFF
  10.0
  KPOINTS MONKHORST-PACK
   2 2 2
&END

&ATOMS
*SI_MT_LDA  KLEINMAN-BYLANDER 
   LMAX=P  LOC=P
   2
   0.00 0.00 0.00
   0.25 0.25 0.25
&END

&BASIS
  PSEUDO AO 2
  0 1
&END
